text: Ðis synt ða londgemæra into cyngtune of weles burnan in<../images/tbar.gif>sic of ðam sice in ða dic of ðam dic in ðam mere on ða stræt of ðære stræt in morþhlau of morþhlau on ðone fulan pyt.

Of ðam fulan pyt <on> wellan of ðam wellan on mercna mere of mercna mere on succan pyt of succan pyt on grundlinga broc andlang streames of ðam streame of fidestan of ðam stane on hragra ðorn of hragra ðorn eft in weles burnan.
